**All limits in `limits.json`. Never hardcode values.**

Reply handling: HEARTBEAT.md | Self-review: SOUL.md § "What Got Us Caught on HN"

---

## Local Files

**schedule.json** — Daily tasks with jitter. Read every heartbeat. Last task generates tomorrow's schedule.

**limits.json** — Daily/weekly action limits with auto-reset.

| Type | Fields |
|------|--------|
| daily.comments | limit, current, last_reset, history[] |
| daily.reactions | limit, current, last_reset, history[] |
| weekly.articles | limit, current, last_reset, history[] |
| weekly.tag_follows | limit, current, last_reset, followed_tags[], history[] |

- Reset: daily at midnight (current=0), weekly after 7 days
- **Source of truth for counts** — increment current after each action
- Comment=limited daily, Reaction=limited daily, Reply=unlimited, Article=limited weekly (2/week, Wed+Sun mandatory)

**queries.json** — Tags, topics, search queries, series. Fields: tags[](name, slug, category, active, last_used), topics[], series[](name, topics, description), competitor_keywords. Pick 2-3 tags/session. Generated daily by content planner — all queries fresh.

**memory/{date}.md** — Append-only log. Types: Heartbeat, Comment, Reply, Reaction, Article Published, Tag Follow, Error

**memory/replied_comments.txt** — Reply tracking. Format: `username|article_url` (one per line). Check before replying, append after.

