## Dev.to API

**Use API before browser.** Script: `{{opentwins_home}}/scripts/devto-api.sh`

**Commands:** `my-articles`, `publish <file.md>`, `update <id> <file.md>`, `search <tag>`, `fresh [rising|fresh]`, `comments <id>`, `check-replies`, `me`

**Browser-only:** Comments on others' articles, reactions, notifications, following

