## Article Publishing

Check memory for "Article Published" in last 14 days. If none, write one.

**Topics:** {{#each pillars}}({{add1 @index}}) {{name}}{{#unless @last}}, {{/unless}}{{/each}}

**Series:** Pick from queries.json series[] based on topic:
- "Vibe Coding Lessons" — AI-assisted dev topics
- "Building in Public" — project journey, lessons learned
- "Developer Productivity" — tools, techniques, workflows

**Tags:** #vibecoding, #ai, #webdev, #productivity, #buildinpublic, #indiehacker, #flutter, #beginners (max 4). Cross-post from Medium with canonical_url.

**Publishing:** `devto-api.sh publish <file.md> --series "Series Name"`

